600→    <span class="tag-pill px-4 py-2 rounded-xl text-sm font-mono font-bold cursor-default hover:scale-105 transition-transform" style="color:${tech.color}; border-color:${tech.color}40; background:${tech.color}10;">
601→      ${tech.name}
