## Part 5: Implementation Sequence

The work should be done in this specific order to avoid conflicts:

### Step 1: Archive current state
1. Copy `DHGSVR25/index.html` to `DHGSVR25/index-v1-dark.html`
2. Take a browser screenshot of the current dark page and save as `REDACTED.png`
3. Commit: "Archive DHGSVR25 v1 dark theme before redesign"

### Step 2: Apply light theme to DHGSVR25/index.html
1. Add the `<style>` block with light theme CSS variable overrides into `<head>` (after the `<link>` tag)
2. Verify visually that all elements look correct on white background
3. Verify the root `index.html` still has its dark theme (load both in browser tabs)
4. Take a screenshot and save as `DHGSVR25/screenshots/archive/v2-light-full.png`
5. Commit: "Apply light theme to DHGSVR25 via CSS variable overrides"

### Step 3: Add flipbook animation to DHGSVR25/index.html
1. Add `<div id="flipbook-overlay">` after `<body>`
2. Add `<noscript>` fallback in `<head>`
3. Add flipbook CSS to the existing `<style>` block
4. Add `<script>` before `</body>` with the flipbook logic
5. Test: verify animation plays, images load, transition works
6. Test: verify page works with JS disabled (overlay hidden by noscript)
7. Commit: "Add flipbook landing animation with 23 student screenshots"

### Step 4: Create making-of page
1. Create `DHGSVR25/screenshots/archive/` directory
2. Create `DHGSVR25/making-of.html` with changelog content
3. Add the subtle footer link in `DHGSVR25/index.html`
4. Verify links work (making-of -> index, making-of -> v1-dark, index -> making-of)
5. Commit: "Add making-of changelog page with version history"

### Step 5: Write blog markdown
1. Create `REDACTED.md`
2. Commit: "Add blog notes documenting DHGSVR25 build process"

