- `/Users/aki/git.local/DHGSVR/DHGSVR25/index.html` - Primary file to modify: add flipbook overlay HTML, light theme CSS overrides, flipbook JavaScript, and footer link to making-of page
- `/Users/aki/git.local/DHGSVR/assets/styles.css` - Must NOT be modified (shared with root dark theme), but must be read carefully to identify all hardcoded rgba values that need overriding in the inline style block
- `/Users/aki/git.local/DHGSVR/DHGSVR25/making-of.html` - New file to create: changelog page with version history, before/after comparison, and technical notes
